{"tid":1879992,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果聽日立法會就23條進行二讀、三讀，大家有無信心阻止到？","createTime":"2020-02-14T13:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T04:36:31.000Z","uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f209784c0410e5bd2b049a273d21eb4db736919","tid":1879992,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"喺星期三進行二讀三讀，早上十一點開會。<br />\n和理非返晒工，得一萬個真勇武（full gear+所有魔法+肯同popo正面打）、四萬個偽勇武（full gear，一衝即退）<br />\n一萬個防暴+二百隻速龍+三架警嫂喺金鐘一帶駐守<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2aouY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2aouY4.jpg&h=5460e720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黨鐵站唔停金鐘站。中環站、香港站、灣仔站、巴士站、每個街口都有防暴（灰叉=100防暴）check bag<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5mJQUqP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5mJQUqP.jpg&h=bdb31008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二幅圖入面黑叉（500防暴+20速龍）見人就打<br />\n假設popo會用正常程度武力，唔用實彈/震撼彈<br />\n親中派議員將會喺10點由校巴護送到立法會<br />\n大家嘅目標就係阻止親中派議員開會至下午五點<br />\n大家覺得有無勝算？"},{"pid":"6e5e768621a9c5da00a31439d2da9ff0871d0a25","tid":1879992,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"要返工 不了"},{"pid":"e41e34a1391805fd79fe38fc9c2f167ba7ad87be","tid":1879992,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e5e768621a9c5da00a31439d2da9ff0871d0a25","tid":1879992,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"要返工 不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:59:37.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a030bbaf051701e3b05631e43607d360e2c4322f","tid":1879992,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"明天星期六"},{"pid":"cdfe0317100729e32e9582c94a50f88fe37c5634","tid":1879992,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a030bbaf051701e3b05631e43607d360e2c4322f","tid":1879992,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"明天星期六"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:01:08.000Z","msg":"用612做參考"},{"pid":"4850090f5a9efe30c91866d69b4677211b8f38a3","tid":1879992,"uid":79655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:03:06.000Z","msg":"難啲"},{"pid":"6135c47f4ee270f536aa6e7dd151065a71484d9c","tid":1879992,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"輸硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f42a5f5687f9b501dd21d51eed3a3e713879efe","tid":1879992,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4850090f5a9efe30c91866d69b4677211b8f38a3","tid":1879992,"uid":79655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:03:06.000Z","msg":"難啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"移民算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b781240b97246268ce20bca3dc7775e02ac24d","tid":1879992,"uid":269202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"講真，夜晚中聯辦開緊急會，全部用緊急法<br />\n<br />\n你都吹佢唔脹啦"},{"pid":"5e1a48931a77fb55be7e0f23777510f744c92ee4","tid":1879992,"uid":160176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"以現在的戰力、戰術、統率方法及火力，<strong>不可能</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果有足夠數量的貨車司機（大部分藍屍）、鄉黑倒戈<br />\n或許勝算會多1-2%&hellip;"},{"pid":"adfe8b89de5d53d1d2dd644e124e6a9dd8510c3a","tid":1879992,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"戰術PO，還是推一下。"},{"pid":"11bdc7dd29a045d9f5425e4cfa1e275ff0f4714c","tid":1879992,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29c0c7df792fd380e831b68c18ffaff689629c9e","tid":1879992,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:12:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e721aacf05fc584ccff75743115d910b3